.theme-light.value: linear-gradient( to top, hsl( calc(215 - 2), 79%, calc(50% - 4%) ) 0px, hsla( calc(215 - 10), 79%, 50%, 20% ) 0px, var(--background-primary) 100% )

.theme-dark.value: linear-gradient( to top, hsl( calc(215 - 2), 79%, calc(50% - 4%) ) 0px, hsla( calc(215 - 10), 79%, 50%, 20% ) 0px, var(--background-primary) 100% )

.workspace-ribbon.mod-left:before.value: linear-gradient( to top, hsl( calc(215 - 2), 79%, calc(50% - 4%) ) 0px, hsla( calc(215 - 10), 79%, 50%, 20% ) 0px, var(--background-primary) 100% )

.mod-rtl.value: linear-gradient( to right, transparent var(--size-4-6), black var(--size-4-6) )

.workspace-leaf-resize-handle.value: background-color 200ms ease-in-out, border-color 200ms ease-in-out, opacity 200ms ease-in-out

.workspace-tab-header-container.value: linear-gradient( to top, hsl( calc(215 - 2), 79%, calc(50% - 4%) ) 0px, hsla( calc(215 - 10), 79%, 50%, 20% ) 0px, var(--background-primary) 100% )

.checkbox-container.value: box-shadow 0.15s ease-in-out, outline 0.15s ease-in-out, border 0.15s ease-in-out, opacity 0.15s ease-in-out

.checkbox-container:after.value: transform 0.15s ease-in-out, width 0.1s ease-in-out, left 0.1s ease-in-out

.theme-dark .pdf-container.mod-themed .p.value: drop-shadow(0px 0px 1px rgb(179, 181, 193)) drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)) drop-shadow(0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4))

.popupWrapper > div.value: drop-shadow(0px 0px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)) drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)) drop-shadow(0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3))

.bases-thead .bases-td[data-sort] .bases.value: linear-gradient( to right, transparent var(--size-4-6), black var(--size-4-6) )

.mobile-navbar-text.value: linear-gradient( to left, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) var(--size-4-4), #000000 var(--size-4-8) )

.is-mobile .prompt.value: min( var(--prompt-max-height), calc(100vh - calc( 59px + var(--header-height) + var(--size-4-2) ) - 34px) )
